local a={"Victory and defeat are omnipresent, even in a relaxing field trip...","Since it is a dream, anything uncanny could happen...","It is always a good thing to meet a friend in a foreign country...","Ah... Good grief, this Shrine is bigger than expected...","The best time for a fierce battle is always late at night, as time is not an issue...","Please do not forget your belongings while leaving...","A genius was born from that same darkness after a rainy night...","The madman has awakened. Just as he\'s about to lose everything…","Love is, in fact, a war!","The battle of wits on love has now become a pure, heated battle of Mahjong, and the battle continues…","And everybody is a winner today.","Although it\'s strange, it\'s quite... unique...","When the girl awakens, the battlefield is waiting for her.","We thought of the same thing~"}return a